When generating reports about changes, readmes, explanations:

1. Place the .md files to @/docs folder
2. Follow GitHub Markdown format
3. Add prefix to filename: `YYYYMMDD_`. ALWAYS generate the timestamps using python: `python -c "from datetime import datetime; print(datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d'))"`
